title: Brie Larson & Jessie Ennis
itunes:title: Brie Larson & Jessie Ennis
itunes:subtitle: Brie Larson [Captain Marvel, Room, Kong: Skull Island, Unicorn Store] and Jessie Ennis [Mythic Quest, Better Call Saul, Life of the Party, Veep] talk with Anna about being best friends since childhood, their new podcast Learning Lots, first kisses, reject
description:
Brie Larson [Captain Marvel, Room, Kong: Skull Island, Unicorn Store] and Jessie Ennis [Mythic Quest, Better Call Saul, Life of the Party, Veep] talk with Anna about being best friends since childhood, their new podcast Learning Lots, first kisses, rejection, love, knitting socks, auditioning, the Academy Awards journey, driving a taxi-cab, losing your phone in a taxi-cab, a haunted purse and more. Later in the episode Anna is joined by best selling author Rachel Hollis who has some great insight on dating during (and after) a pandemic.
